+TinyNav Jetson command reference
+Last updated: 2026-06-16
+Repo: /home/nvidia/twork/tinynav
+Symlink: /tinynav
+
+===============================================================================
+0. Base environment
+===============================================================================
+
+source /home/nvidia/twork/tinynav_setup.bash
+cd /home/nvidia/twork/tinynav
+
+# Optional Python venv activation for direct Python work.
+source /home/nvidia/twork/tinynav/.venv/bin/activate
+
+# Quick status.
+git status --short
+ros2 topic list | sort
+
+===============================================================================
+1. Minimal daily flow
+===============================================================================
+
+# Build a fresh map from RealSense.
+# Walk slowly. Press Ctrl-C once to stop recording; the script then validates
+# the bag and builds the map.
+source /home/nvidia/twork/tinynav_setup.bash
+cd /home/nvidia/twork/tinynav
+bash scripts/tinynav_auto_map.sh
+
+# Latest map symlink.
+ls -lah /home/nvidia/twork/tinynav/output/latest_map
+
+# Start navigation using output/latest_map.
+# This starts RViz, TinyNav nodes, RViz-goal-to-POI bridge, diagnostics, and
+# the Go2 bridge by default.
+source /home/nvidia/twork/tinynav_setup.bash
+cd /home/nvidia/twork/tinynav
+bash scripts/tinynav_auto_nav.sh
+
+# Start navigation without sending /cmd_vel to Go2.
+bash scripts/tinynav_auto_nav.sh --no-go2
+
+# Use a specific map.
+bash scripts/tinynav_auto_nav.sh --map /home/nvidia/twork/tinynav/output/latest_map
