+===============================================================================
+6. RViz goal to TinyNav POI
+===============================================================================
+
+# In RViz, use "2D Goal Pose". The bridge converts /goal_pose into:
+#   <map>/pois.json
+#   /mapping/cmd_pois
+#   /rviz_goal_pose_marker
+#   /rviz_goal_marker
